  ('promotion-bd450684-moex-00069', 'promotion-bd450684', 'promotion-bd450684-moex-110-de0a21a2', 'sub-promotion-bd450684-01', NULL, 'essay', '甲假冒警察身分身穿警察反光夾克，騎乘機車靠近 14 歲少女乙，之後在
